{"data":[{"name":"53:1","price":"1. விழுந்து மறையும் நட்சத்திரத்தின் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّجۡمِ إِذَا هَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4785,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-najmi idhā hawā ","translations":["By the star","when","it goes down","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-najmi","idhā","hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2350],[2,2350,2980],[3,2980,3855]]}},{"name":"53:2","price":"2. (நம் தூதராகிய) உங்கள் தோழர் வழி தவறி விடவுமில்லை; தவறான வழியில் செல்லவுமில்லை.","arabic":"مَا ضَلَّ صَاحِبُكُمۡ وَمَا غَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4786,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mā ḍalla ṣāḥibukum wamā ghawā ","translations":["Not","has strayed","your companion","and not","has he erred","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","ḍalla","ṣāḥibukum","wamā","ghawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1170],[3,1170,2600],[4,2600,3320],[5,3320,4125]]}},{"name":"53:3","price":"3. அவர் தன் விருப்பப்படி எதையும் கூறுவதில்லை.","arabic":"وَمَا يَنطِقُ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4787,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yanṭiqu ʿani al-hawā ","translations":["And not","he speaks","from","the desire","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yanṭiqu","ʿani","al-hawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,2560],[3,2560,2930],[4,2930,4025]]}},{"name":"53:4","price":"4. இது அவருக்கு வஹ்யி மூலம் அறிவிக்கப்பட்டதே தவிர (வேறு) இல்லை.","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا وَحۡيٞ يُوحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4788,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"in huwa illā waḥyun yūḥā ","translations":["Not","it","(is) except","a revelation","revealed","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["in","huwa","illā","waḥyun","yūḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,470],[2,470,800],[3,800,1800],[4,1800,2550],[5,2550,4355]]}},{"name":"53:5","price":"5. (ஜிப்ரயீல் என்னும்) வலுவான ஆற்றலுடையவர் இதை அவருக்குக் கற்றுக் கொடுக்கிறார்.","arabic":"عَلَّمَهُۥ شَدِيدُ ٱلۡقُوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4789,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallamahu shadīdu al-quwā ","translations":["Has taught him","the (one) mighty","(in) power","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallamahu","shadīdu","al-quwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,2570],[3,2570,3445]]}},{"name":"53:6","price":"6. அவர் மிக்க ஆத்ம சக்தியுடையவர். அவர் (தன் இயற்கை ரூபத்தில் நபி முன்) தோன்றினார்.","arabic":"ذُو مِرَّةٖ فَٱسۡتَوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4790,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū mirratin fa-is'tawā ","translations":["Possessor of soundness","Possessor of soundness","And he rose","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","mirratin","fa-is'tawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,560],[2,560,1950],[3,1950,3835]]}},{"name":"53:7","price":"7. அவர் உயர்ந்த (வானத்தின்) கடைக்கோடியில் இருந்தார்.","arabic":"وَهُوَ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4791,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa bil-ufuqi al-aʿlā ","translations":["While he","(was) in the horizon ","the highest","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","bil-ufuqi","al-aʿlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,1850],[3,1850,3115]]}},{"name":"53:8","price":"8. இன்னும் நெருங்கினார், (அவர் முன்) இறங்கினார். ","arabic":"ثُمَّ دَنَا فَتَدَلَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4792,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma danā fatadallā ","translations":["Then","he approached","and came down","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","danā","fatadallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,2000],[3,2000,3475]]}},{"name":"53:9","price":"9. (சேர்ந்த) இரு வில்களைப்போல், அல்லது அதைவிட சமீபமாக அவர் நெருங்கினார்.","arabic":"فَكَانَ قَابَ قَوۡسَيۡنِ أَوۡ أَدۡنَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4793,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fakāna qāba qawsayni aw adnā ","translations":["And was","(at) a distance","(of) two bow-(lengths)","or","nearer","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fakāna","qāba","qawsayni","aw","adnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1640],[3,1640,2850],[4,2850,3250],[5,3250,4235]]}},{"name":"53:10","price":"10. (அல்லாஹ்) அவருக்கு (வஹ்யி மூலம்) அறிவித்ததையெல்லாம் அவர் அவனுடைய (நபியாகிய) அடியாருக்கு அறிவித்தார்.","arabic":"فَأَوۡحَىٰٓ إِلَىٰ عَبۡدِهِۦ مَآ أَوۡحَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4794,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-awḥā ilā ʿabdihi mā awḥā ","translations":["So he revealed","to","His slave","what","he revealed","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-awḥā","ilā","ʿabdihi","mā","awḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2510],[2,2510,3160],[3,3160,4330],[4,4330,4510],[5,4510,5960],[6,5960,7045]]}},{"name":"53:11","price":"11. (நபியுடைய) உள்ளம், தான் கண்டதைப் பற்றிப் பொய் கூறவில்லை. ","arabic":"مَا كَذَبَ ٱلۡفُؤَادُ مَا رَأَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4795,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mā kadhaba al-fuādu mā raā ","translations":["Not","lied","the heart","what","it saw","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","kadhaba","al-fuādu","mā","raā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,480],[2,480,1150],[3,1150,2370],[4,2370,2830],[5,2830,3565]]}},{"name":"53:12","price":"12. அவர் கண்டதைப் பற்றி நீங்கள் (சந்தேகித்து) அவருடன் தர்க்கிக்கிறீர்களா?","arabic":"أَفَتُمَٰرُونَهُۥ عَلَىٰ مَا يَرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4796,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afatumārūnahu ʿalā mā yarā ","translations":["Then will you dispute with him","about","what","he saw","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["afatumārūnahu","ʿalā","mā","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,3100],[3,3100,3570],[4,3570,4875]]}},{"name":"53:13","price":"13. நிச்சயமாக அவர், மற்றொரு முறையும் (தன்னிடத்தில் ஜிப்ரயீலாகிய) அவர் இறங்கக் கண்டிருக்கிறார்.","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ نَزۡلَةً أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4797,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walaqad raāhu nazlatan ukh'rā ","translations":["And certainly","he saw him","(in) descent","another","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["walaqad","raāhu","nazlatan","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1810],[3,1810,2950],[4,2950,4395]]}},{"name":"53:14","price":"14. ‘‘ஸித்ரத்துல் முன்தஹா' என்னும் (இலந்தை) மரத்தின் சமீபத்தில்.","arabic":"عِندَ سِدۡرَةِ ٱلۡمُنتَهَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4798,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿinda sid'rati al-muntahā ","translations":["Near","(the) Lote Tree","(of) the utmost boundary","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿinda","sid'rati","al-muntahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2410],[3,2410,4665]]}},{"name":"53:15","price":"15. அதன் சமீபத்தில்தான் (நல்லடியார்கள்) தங்கும் சொர்க்கம் இருக்கிறது. ","arabic":"عِندَهَا جَنَّةُ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4799,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿindahā jannatu al-mawā ","translations":["Near it","(is the) Garden","(of) Abode","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿindahā","jannatu","al-mawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,3670],[3,3670,4965]]}},{"name":"53:16","price":"16. அந்த மரத்தை மூடியிருந்தவை அதை முற்றிலும் மூடிக்கொண்டன.","arabic":"إِذۡ يَغۡشَى ٱلسِّدۡرَةَ مَا يَغۡشَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4800,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idh yaghshā al-sid'rata mā yaghshā ","translations":["When","covered","the Lote Tree","what","covers","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","yaghshā","al-sid'rata","mā","yaghshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1090],[3,1090,2330],[4,2330,2780],[5,2780,3835]]}},{"name":"53:17","price":"17. (அதிலிருந்து அவருடைய) பார்வை விலகவும் இல்லை; கடக்கவும் இல்லை!","arabic":"مَا زَاغَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ وَمَا طَغَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4801,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"mā zāgha al-baṣaru wamā ṭaghā ","translations":["Not","swerved","the sight","and not","it transgressed","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","zāgha","al-baṣaru","wamā","ṭaghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1220],[3,1220,2150],[4,2150,2630],[5,2630,4275]]}},{"name":"53:18","price":"18. அவர் தன் இறைவனின் மிகப்பெரிய அத்தாட்சிகளையெல்லாம் மெய்யாகவே கண்டார்.","arabic":"لَقَدۡ رَأَىٰ مِنۡ ءَايَٰتِ رَبِّهِ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4802,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"laqad raā min āyāti rabbihi al-kub'rā ","translations":["Certainly","he saw","of","(the) Signs","(of) his Lord","the Greatest","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["laqad","raā","min","āyāti","rabbihi","al-kub'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1390],[3,1390,1830],[4,1830,3160],[5,3160,3980],[6,3980,5725]]}},{"name":"53:19","price":"19. (நீங்கள் ஆராதனை செய்யும்) லாத், உஜ்ஜா (என்னும் சிலை)களை நீங்கள் கவனித்தீர்களா?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتُمُ ٱللَّٰتَ وَٱلۡعُزَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4803,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afara-aytumu al-lāta wal-ʿuzā ","translations":["So have you seen","the Lat","and the Uzza","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["afara-aytumu","al-lāta","wal-ʿuzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1630],[2,1630,2720],[3,2720,4195]]}},{"name":"53:20","price":"20. மற்றொரு மூன்றாவது மனாத் (என்னும் சிலையைப்) பற்றியும் நீங்கள் சிந்தித்தீர்களா? (அவற்றுக்கு ஏதேனும் இத்தகைய சக்தி உண்டா?)","arabic":"وَمَنَوٰةَ ٱلثَّالِثَةَ ٱلۡأُخۡرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4804,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamanata al-thālithata al-ukh'rā ","translations":["And Manat","the third","the other","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["wamanata","al-thālithata","al-ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2600],[3,2600,4525]]}},{"name":"53:21","price":"21. என்னே! உங்களுக்கு ஆண் மக்கள், அவனுக்குப் பெண் மக்களா?","arabic":"أَلَكُمُ ٱلذَّكَرُ وَلَهُ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4805,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alakumu al-dhakaru walahu al-unthā ","translations":["Is for you","the male","and for Him","the female","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["alakumu","al-dhakaru","walahu","al-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1910],[3,1910,2590],[4,2590,4775]]}},{"name":"53:22","price":"22. அவ்வாறாயின், அது மிக்க அநியாயமான பங்கீடாகும்.","arabic":"تِلۡكَ إِذٗا قِسۡمَةٞ ضِيزَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4806,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"til'ka idhan qis'matun ḍīzā ","translations":["This","then","(is) a division","unfair","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["til'ka","idhan","qis'matun","ḍīzā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2180],[3,2180,4430],[4,4430,5565]]}},{"name":"53:23","price":"23. இவையெல்லாம் நீங்களும், உங்கள் மூதாதைகளும் வைத்துக் கொண்ட வெறும் பெயர்களே தவிர (அவை வணங்கத் தகுதியானவை) இல்லை. அ(வை வணங்கத் தகுதியானவை என்ப)தற்காக அல்லாஹ் உங்களுக்கு எந்த ஆதாரத்தையும் (முந்திய வேதங்களிலும்) இறக்கிவைக்கவில்லை. அவர்கள் (தங்கள்) மன இச்சைகளையும் வீண் சந்தேகத்தையும் தவிர, (இறை வேதத்தை பின்பற்றுவது) இல்லை. நிச்சயமாக அவர்களுடைய இறைவனிடமிருந்து அவர்களுக்கு நேரான வழி (இந்த குர்ஆன்) வந்தே இருக்கிறது. (எனினும், அதை அவர்கள் பின்பற்றுவதில்லை.)","arabic":"إِنۡ هِيَ إِلَّآ أَسۡمَآءٞ سَمَّيۡتُمُوهَآ أَنتُمۡ وَءَابَآؤُكُم مَّآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَا مِن سُلۡطَٰنٍۚ إِن يَتَّبِعُونَ إِلَّا ٱلظَّنَّ وَمَا تَهۡوَى ٱلۡأَنفُسُۖ وَلَقَدۡ جَآءَهُم مِّن رَّبِّهِمُ ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4807,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"in hiya illā asmāon sammaytumūhā antum waābāukum mā anzala al-lahu bihā min sul'ṭānin in yattabiʿūna illā al-ẓana wamā tahwā al-anfusu walaqad jāahum min rabbihimu al-hudā ","translations":["Not","they","(are) except","names","you have named them","you","and your forefathers","not","has Allah sent down","has Allah sent down","for it","any","authority","Not","they follow","except","assumption","and what","desire","the(ir) souls","And certainly","has come to them","from","their Lord","the guidance","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["in","hiya","illā","asmāon","sammaytumūhā","antum","waābāukum","mā","anzala","al-lahu","bihā","min","sul'ṭānin","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wamā","tahwā","al-anfusu","walaqad","jāahum","min","rabbihimu","al-hudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,930],[3,930,3080],[4,3080,6460],[5,6460,9370],[6,9370,14280],[7,14280,15980],[8,15980,19500],[9,19500,21410],[10,21410,22810],[11,22810,23910],[12,23910,24560],[13,24560,24920],[14,24920,25760],[15,25760,29440],[16,29440,30390],[17,30390,31870],[18,31870,32570],[19,32570,34170],[20,34170,34810],[21,34810,35510],[22,35510,37820],[23,37820,39200],[24,39200,42030],[25,42030,43140],[26,43140,44520],[27,44520,45645]]}},{"name":"53:24","price":"24. மனிதன் விரும்பியதெல்லாம் அவனுக்குக் கிடைத்துவிடுமா?","arabic":"أَمۡ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ مَا تَمَنَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4808,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"am lil'insāni mā tamannā ","translations":["Or","(is) for man","what","he wishes","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lil'insāni","mā","tamannā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,2850],[3,2850,3250],[4,3250,5335]]}},{"name":"53:25","price":"25. (ஏனென்றால்) இம்மையும் மறுமையும் அல்லாஹ்வுக்குறியனவே! (அவன் விரும்பியவர்களுக்கே அவற்றின் பாக்கியத்தை அளிப்பான்.)","arabic":"فَلِلَّهِ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةُ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4809,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"falillahi al-ākhiratu wal-ūlā ","translations":["But for Allah","(is) the last","and the first","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["falillahi","al-ākhiratu","wal-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,2790],[3,2790,4145]]}},{"name":"53:26","price":"26. வானத்தில் எத்தனையோ வானவர்கள் இருக்கின்றனர். (எவருக்காகவும்)அவர்கள் பரிந்து பேசுவது ஒரு பயனும் அளிக்காது. ஆயினும், அல்லாஹ் விரும்பி, எவரைப் பற்றித் திருப்தியடைந்து (அவருக்காக) அவன் அனுமதி கொடுக்கிறானோ அவருக்கே தவிர (மற்றவருக்கு பயனளிக்காது).","arabic":"۞ وَكَم مِّن مَّلَكٖ فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ لَا تُغۡنِي شَفَٰعَتُهُمۡ شَيۡـًٔا إِلَّا مِنۢ بَعۡدِ أَن يَأۡذَنَ ٱللَّهُ لِمَن يَشَآءُ وَيَرۡضَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4810,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wakam min malakin fī al-samāwāti lā tugh'nī shafāʿatuhum shayan illā min baʿdi an yadhana al-lahu liman yashāu wayarḍā ","translations":["And how many","of","(the) Angels","in","the heavens","not","will avail","their intercession","anything","except","after","after","[that]","Allah has given permission","Allah has given permission","for whom","He wills","and approves","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wakam","min","malakin","fī","al-samāwāti","lā","tugh'nī","shafāʿatuhum","shayan","illā","min","baʿdi","an","yadhana","al-lahu","liman","yashāu","wayarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,1590],[3,1590,3940],[4,3940,4260],[5,4260,5940],[6,5940,6350],[7,6350,7190],[8,7190,8850],[9,8850,10480],[10,10480,10890],[11,10890,11790],[12,11790,13390],[13,13390,14340],[14,14340,15330],[15,15330,16620],[16,16620,17280],[17,17280,17580],[18,17580,18250],[19,18250,19010],[20,19010,20100],[21,20100,20470],[22,20470,21130],[23,21130,23490],[24,23490,24785]]}},{"name":"53:27","price":"27. நிச்சயமாக எவர்கள் மறுமையை நம்பிக்கை கொள்ளவில்லையோ, அவர்கள் வானவர்களுக்குப் பெண்களின் பெயர்களை சூட்டுகின்றனர்.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤۡمِنُونَ بِٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ لَيُسَمُّونَ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ تَسۡمِيَةَ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4811,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna lā yu'minūna bil-ākhirati layusammūna al-malāikata tasmiyata al-unthā ","translations":["Indeed","those who","(do) not","believe","in the Hereafter","surely they name","the Angels","name(s)","(of) female","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","lā","yu'minūna","bil-ākhirati","layusammūna","al-malāikata","tasmiyata","al-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1720],[2,1720,2850],[3,2850,3370],[4,3370,4740],[5,4740,6420],[6,6420,8710],[7,8710,11860],[8,11860,12920],[9,12920,15075]]}},{"name":"53:28","price":"28. இதைப் பற்றி அவர்களுக்கு ஒரு ஞானமும் கிடையாது. (ஆதாரமற்ற) வீண் சந்தேகத்தைத் தவிர (வேறு எதையும்) அவர்கள் பின்பற்றுவதில்லை. வீண் சந்தேகம் எதையும் உறுதிப்படுத்தாது.","arabic":"وَمَا لَهُم بِهِۦ مِنۡ عِلۡمٍۖ إِن يَتَّبِعُونَ إِلَّا ٱلظَّنَّۖ وَإِنَّ ٱلظَّنَّ لَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱلۡحَقِّ شَيۡـٔٗا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4812,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā lahum bihi min ʿil'min in yattabiʿūna illā al-ẓana wa-inna al-ẓana lā yugh'nī mina al-ḥaqi shayan ","translations":["And not","for them","about it","any","knowledge","Not","they follow","but","assumption","And indeed","the assumption","(does) not","avail","against","the truth","anything","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","lahum","bihi","min","ʿil'min","in","yattabiʿūna","illā","al-ẓana","wa-inna","al-ẓana","lā","yugh'nī","mina","al-ḥaqi","shayan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,670],[2,670,2209],[3,2209,2920],[4,2920,3350],[5,3350,4520],[6,4520,5740],[7,5740,7240],[8,7240,7870],[9,7870,9650],[10,9650,11000],[11,11000,12350],[12,12350,12820],[13,12820,13730],[14,13730,14170],[15,14170,15090],[16,15090,16145]]}},{"name":"53:29","price":"29. (நபியே!) எவன் என்னைத் தியானிக்காது விலகி, இவ்வுலக வாழ்க்கையைத் தவிர, (மறுமையை) விரும்பாதிருக்கிறானோ, அவனை நீர் புறக்கணித்து விடுவீராக.","arabic":"فَأَعۡرِضۡ عَن مَّن تَوَلَّىٰ عَن ذِكۡرِنَا وَلَمۡ يُرِدۡ إِلَّا ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4813,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-aʿriḍ ʿan man tawallā ʿan dhik'rinā walam yurid illā al-ḥayata al-dun'yā ","translations":["So turn away","from","(him) who","turns away","from","Our Reminder","and not","he desires","except","the life","(of) the world","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-aʿriḍ","ʿan","man","tawallā","ʿan","dhik'rinā","walam","yurid","illā","al-ḥayata","al-dun'yā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1080],[2,1080,1370],[3,1370,2900],[4,2900,4050],[5,4050,5080],[6,5080,6190],[7,6190,6870],[8,6870,7560],[9,7560,8160],[10,8160,9310],[11,9310,10535]]}},{"name":"53:30","price":"30. இவர்களுடைய கல்வி ஞானம் இவ்வளவு தூரம்தான் செல்கிறது (இதற்கு மேல் செல்வதில்லை.) நிச்சயமாக உமது இறைவன், தன் வழியிலிருந்து தவறியவன் யாரென்பதையும் நன்கறிவான். நேரான வழியில் செல்பவன் யாரென்பதையும் அவன் நன்கறிவான்.","arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ مَبۡلَغُهُم مِّنَ ٱلۡعِلۡمِۚ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَن ضَلَّ عَن سَبِيلِهِۦ وَهُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَنِ ٱهۡتَدَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4814,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"dhālika mablaghuhum mina al-ʿil'mi inna rabbaka huwa aʿlamu biman ḍalla ʿan sabīlihi wahuwa aʿlamu bimani ih'tadā ","translations":["That","(is) their sum","of","knowledge","Indeed","your Lord","(is) He (Who)","knows best","(he) who","strays","from","His Path","and He","knows best","(he) who","is guided","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["dhālika","mablaghuhum","mina","al-ʿil'mi","inna","rabbaka","huwa","aʿlamu","biman","ḍalla","ʿan","sabīlihi","wahuwa","aʿlamu","bimani","ih'tadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,2180],[3,2180,3410],[4,3410,4700],[5,4700,5690],[6,5690,6640],[7,6640,6960],[8,6960,7980],[9,7980,9200],[10,9200,9850],[11,9850,10790],[12,10790,12200],[13,12200,12880],[14,12880,13830],[15,13830,14510],[16,14510,15565]]}},{"name":"53:31","price":"31. வானங்களிலுள்ளவை, பூமியிலுள்ளவை அனைத்தும் அல்லாஹ்வுக்கு உரியனவே. ஆகவே, தீமை செய்தவர்களுக்கு அவர்களுடைய (தீய) செயலுக்குத் தக்கவாறு (தீமையைக்) கூலியாகக் கொடுக்கிறான். நன்மை செய்தவர்களுக்கு நன்மையைக் கூலியாகக் கொடுக்கிறான்.","arabic":"وَلِلَّهِ مَا فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ لِيَجۡزِيَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَسَٰٓـُٔواْ بِمَا عَمِلُواْ وَيَجۡزِيَ ٱلَّذِينَ أَحۡسَنُواْ بِٱلۡحُسۡنَى","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4815,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walillahi mā fī al-samāwāti wamā fī al-arḍi liyajziya alladhīna asāū bimā ʿamilū wayajziya alladhīna aḥsanū bil-ḥus'nā ","translations":["And for Allah","(is) whatever","(is) in","the heavens","and whatever","(is) in","the earth","that He may recompense","those who","do evil","with what","they have done","and recompense","those who","do good","with the best","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["walillahi","mā","fī","al-samāwāti","wamā","fī","al-arḍi","liyajziya","alladhīna","asāū","bimā","ʿamilū","wayajziya","alladhīna","aḥsanū","bil-ḥus'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,1820],[3,1820,2040],[4,2040,3810],[5,3810,4400],[6,4400,4650],[7,4650,5620],[8,5620,6710],[9,6710,7850],[10,7850,10859],[11,10859,11549],[12,11549,12569],[13,12569,13599],[14,13599,14699],[15,14699,15899],[16,15899,17414]]}},{"name":"53:32","price":"32. (நன்மை செய்யும்) அவர்கள் (ஏதும் தவறாக ஏற்பட்டுவிடும்) அற்பமான பாவங்களைத் தவிர, மற்ற பெரும்பாவங்களிலிருந்தும், மானக்கேடான விஷயங்களிலிருந்தும் விலகியிருப்பார்கள். நிச்சயமாக உமது இறைவன் மன்னிப்பதில் மிக்க தாராளமானவன். உங்களைப் பூமியிலிருந்து உற்பத்தி செய்த சமயத்தில் (உங்கள் தன்மையை) அவன் நன்கறிவான். நீங்கள் உங்கள் தாயின் வயிற்றில் கர்ப்பப்பிண்டமாயிருந்த சமயத்திலும் உங்களை அவன் நன்கறிவான். ஆகவே, ‘‘தூய்மையானவர்கள்' என உங்களை நீங்களே தற்புகழ்ச்சி செய்துகொள்ளாதீர்கள். உங்களில் அல்லாஹ்வை அஞ்சிக் கொள்பவர்கள் யாரென்பதை அவன் நன்கறிவான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يَجۡتَنِبُونَ كَبَٰٓئِرَ ٱلۡإِثۡمِ وَٱلۡفَوَٰحِشَ إِلَّا ٱللَّمَمَۚ إِنَّ رَبَّكَ وَٰسِعُ ٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِۚ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِكُمۡ إِذۡ أَنشَأَكُم مِّنَ ٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَإِذۡ أَنتُمۡ أَجِنَّةٞ فِي بُطُونِ أُمَّهَٰتِكُمۡۖ فَلَا تُزَكُّوٓاْ أَنفُسَكُمۡۖ هُوَ أَعۡلَمُ بِمَنِ ٱتَّقَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4816,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna yajtanibūna kabāira al-ith'mi wal-fawāḥisha illā al-lamama inna rabbaka wāsiʿu al-maghfirati huwa aʿlamu bikum idh ansha-akum mina al-arḍi wa-idh antum ajinnatun fī buṭūni ummahātikum falā tuzakkū anfusakum huwa aʿlamu bimani ittaqā ","translations":["Those who","avoid","great","sins","and the immoralities","except","the small faults","indeed","your Lord","(is) vast","(in) forgiveness","He","(is) most knowing about you","(is) most knowing about you","when","He produced you","from","the earth","and when","you (were)","fetuses","in","(the) wombs","(of) your mothers","So (do) not","ascribe purity","(to) yourselves","He","knows best","(he) who","fears","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","yajtanibūna","kabāira","al-ith'mi","wal-fawāḥisha","illā","al-lamama","inna","rabbaka","wāsiʿu","al-maghfirati","huwa","aʿlamu","bikum","idh","ansha-akum","mina","al-arḍi","wa-idh","antum","ajinnatun","fī","buṭūni","ummahātikum","falā","tuzakkū","anfusakum","huwa","aʿlamu","bimani","ittaqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,2800],[3,2800,5480],[4,5480,6470],[5,6470,8160],[6,8160,8690],[7,8690,10230],[8,10230,11420],[9,11420,12440],[10,12440,13250],[11,13250,15120],[12,15120,15460],[13,15460,16430],[14,16430,17120],[15,17120,17520],[16,17520,19290],[17,19290,20320],[18,20320,21340],[19,21340,21950],[20,21950,23550],[21,23550,25680],[22,25680,26520],[23,26520,27460],[24,27460,30550],[25,30550,31190],[26,31190,34260],[27,34260,36740],[28,36740,37080],[29,37080,38070],[30,38070,38740],[31,38740,40215]]}},{"name":"53:33","price":"33. (நபியே!) உம்மை விட்டும் விலகியவனை நீர் கவனித்தீரா?","arabic":"أَفَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي تَوَلَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4817,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afara-ayta alladhī tawallā ","translations":["Did you see","the one who","turned away","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["afara-ayta","alladhī","tawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1280],[2,1280,2220],[3,2220,3475]]}},{"name":"53:34","price":"34. அவன் ஒரு சொற்பத்தை தர்மம் கொடுத்துவிட்டு, கொடுப்பதையே (முற்றிலும்) நிறுத்திக் கொண்டான்.","arabic":"وَأَعۡطَىٰ قَلِيلٗا وَأَكۡدَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4818,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-aʿṭā qalīlan wa-akdā ","translations":["And gave","a little","and withheld","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-aʿṭā","qalīlan","wa-akdā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,2180],[3,2180,4165]]}},{"name":"53:35","price":"35. அவனிடத்தில் மறைவான விஷயத்தின் ஞானமிருந்து (தன் முடிவை அதில்) அவன் பார்த்தானா?","arabic":"أَعِندَهُۥ عِلۡمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ فَهُوَ يَرَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4819,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"aʿindahu ʿil'mu al-ghaybi fahuwa yarā ","translations":["Is with him","(the) knowledge","(of) the unseen","so he","sees","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["aʿindahu","ʿil'mu","al-ghaybi","fahuwa","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2490],[3,2490,3390],[4,3390,4130],[5,4130,5345]]}},{"name":"53:36","price":"36. அல்லது மூஸாவுடைய வேதத்திலுள்ளவை அவனுக்கு அறிவிக்கப்படவில்லையா?","arabic":"أَمۡ لَمۡ يُنَبَّأۡ بِمَا فِي صُحُفِ مُوسَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4820,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"am lam yunabba bimā fī ṣuḥufi mūsā ","translations":["Or","not","he was informed","with what","(was) in","(the) Scriptures","(of) Musa","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lam","yunabba","bimā","fī","ṣuḥufi","mūsā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,370],[2,370,830],[3,830,1840],[4,1840,2510],[5,2510,2960],[6,2960,3710],[7,3710,4725]]}},{"name":"53:37","price":"37. (அல்லது இறைவனுடைய கட்டளைகளை) முழுமையாக நிறைவேற்றிய இப்ராஹீமுடைய விஷயமேனும் (அவனுக்குத் தெரியாதா?)","arabic":"وَإِبۡرَٰهِيمَ ٱلَّذِي وَفَّىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4821,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ib'rāhīma alladhī waffā ","translations":["And Ibrahim","who","fulfilled","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ib'rāhīma","alladhī","waffā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1670],[2,1670,2630],[3,2630,3625]]}},{"name":"53:38","price":"38. (நபியே!) அறிந்து கொள்வீராக! ஒருவனின் பாவச் சுமையை மற்றொருவன் சுமக்க மாட்டான்","arabic":"أَلَّا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٞ وِزۡرَ أُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4822,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"allā taziru wāziratun wiz'ra ukh'rā ","translations":["That not","will bear","a bearer of burdens","(the) burden","(of) another","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["allā","taziru","wāziratun","wiz'ra","ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1480],[3,1480,3510],[4,3510,4200],[5,4200,5645]]}},{"name":"53:39","price":"39. ‘‘இன்னும் நிச்சயமாக மனிதனுக்கு அவன் செய்த செயலைத் தவிர வேறொன்றும் கிடைக்காது.''","arabic":"وَأَن لَّيۡسَ لِلۡإِنسَٰنِ إِلَّا مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4823,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-an laysa lil'insāni illā mā saʿā ","translations":["And that","is not","for man","except","what","he strives (for)","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-an","laysa","lil'insāni","illā","mā","saʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1240],[3,1240,3650],[4,3650,4560],[5,4560,4950],[6,4950,5805]]}},{"name":"53:40","price":"40. நிச்சயமாக (மனிதன் செய்த) செயல்தான் கவனிக்கப்படும்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّ سَعۡيَهُۥ سَوۡفَ يُرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4824,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna saʿyahu sawfa yurā ","translations":["And that","his striving","will soon","be seen","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","saʿyahu","sawfa","yurā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,2420],[3,2420,3180],[4,3180,4395]]}},{"name":"53:41","price":"41. பின்னர், செயலுக்குத் தக்க கூலி முழுமையாகக் கொடுக்கப்படுவான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ يُجۡزَىٰهُ ٱلۡجَزَآءَ ٱلۡأَوۡفَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4825,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma yuj'zāhu al-jazāa al-awfā ","translations":["Then","he will be recompensed for it","the recompense","the fullest","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","yuj'zāhu","al-jazāa","al-awfā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,2220],[3,2220,4860],[4,4860,6195]]}},{"name":"53:42","price":"42. (நபியே!) நிச்சயமாக உமது இறைவனிடம்தான் (உங்கள் அனைவரின்) இறுதி இடம் இருக்கிறது.","arabic":"وَأَنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡمُنتَهَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4826,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna ilā rabbika al-muntahā ","translations":["And that","to","your Lord","(is) the final goal","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","ilā","rabbika","al-muntahā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1450],[2,1450,2110],[3,2110,3060],[4,3060,5375]]}},{"name":"53:43","price":"43. நிச்சயமாக அவனே சிரிக்க வைக்கிறான்; அழவும் வைக்கிறான். ","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ أَضۡحَكَ وَأَبۡكَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4827,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa aḍḥaka wa-abkā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","makes (one) laugh","and makes (one) weep","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","aḍḥaka","wa-abkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1850],[2,1850,2270],[3,2270,3270],[4,3270,4385]]}},{"name":"53:44","price":"44. நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான் மரணிக்க வைக்கிறான்; (திரும்பவும்) உயிர்ப்பிக்கிறான்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ أَمَاتَ وَأَحۡيَا","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4828,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa amāta wa-aḥyā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","causes death","and gives life","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","amāta","wa-aḥyā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1950],[2,1950,2300],[3,2300,3320],[4,3320,4525]]}},{"name":"53:45","price":"45. நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான் ஆண், பெண் ஜோடிகளாகப் படைக்கிறான்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ خَلَقَ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4829,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu khalaqa al-zawjayni al-dhakara wal-unthā ","translations":["And that He","created","the pairs","the male","and the female","(45)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","khalaqa","al-zawjayni","al-dhakara","wal-unthā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1930],[2,1930,2620],[3,2620,4020],[4,4020,4930],[5,4930,7045]]}},{"name":"53:46","price":"46. (கர்ப்பத்தில்) செலுத்தப்படும் ஒரு துளி இந்திரியத்தைக் கொண்டே (உங்களைப் படைக்கிறான்).","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ إِذَا تُمۡنَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4830,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min nuṭ'fatin idhā tum'nā ","translations":["From","a semen-drop","when","it is emitted","(46)"],"transliterationArr":["min","nuṭ'fatin","idhā","tum'nā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,300],[2,300,2050],[3,2050,2720],[4,2720,3735]]}},{"name":"53:47","price":"47. நிச்சயமாக (நீங்கள் மரணித்தப் பின்னர் உங்களை) மறுமுறை உயிர் கொடுத்து எழுப்புவதும் அவன் மீது கடமையாக இருக்கிறது.","arabic":"وَأَنَّ عَلَيۡهِ ٱلنَّشۡأَةَ ٱلۡأُخۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4831,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-anna ʿalayhi al-nashata al-ukh'rā ","translations":["And that","upon Him","(is) the bringing forth","another","(47)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-anna","ʿalayhi","al-nashata","al-ukh'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1360],[2,1360,2270],[3,2270,4030],[4,4030,5645]]}},{"name":"53:48","price":"48. பொருளைக் கொடுத்து (அதை நீங்கள்) சேகரித்துச் சீமானாகும்படி செய்பவனும் நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ أَغۡنَىٰ وَأَقۡنَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4832,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa aghnā wa-aqnā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","enriches","and suffices","(48)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","aghnā","wa-aqnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2150],[2,2150,2510],[3,2510,3490],[4,3490,4665]]}},{"name":"53:49","price":"49. (இணைவைப்பவர்களே! நீங்கள் வணங்கும்) ‘ஷிஃரா' என்னும் நட்சத்திரத்தின் இறைவனும் நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥ هُوَ رَبُّ ٱلشِّعۡرَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4833,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu huwa rabbu al-shiʿ'rā ","translations":["And that He","[He]","(is the) Lord","(of) Sirius","(49)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","huwa","rabbu","al-shiʿ'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1770],[2,1770,2140],[3,2140,2850],[4,2850,4415]]}},{"name":"53:50","price":"50. (அந்த நட்சத்திரத்தை வணங்கிக் கொண்டிருந்த) முந்திய ஆது என்னும் மக்களை அழித்தவனும் நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான்.","arabic":"وَأَنَّهُۥٓ أَهۡلَكَ عَادًا ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4834,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-annahu ahlaka ʿādan al-ūlā ","translations":["And that He","destroyed","Aad","the first","(50)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-annahu","ahlaka","ʿādan","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2950],[2,2950,3840],[3,3840,4660],[4,4660,5935]]}},{"name":"53:51","price":"51. ஸமூத் என்னும் மக்களையும் (அழித்தவன் அவன்தான். அவர்களில் ஒருவரையுமே) அவன் தப்பவிடவில்லை.","arabic":"وَثَمُودَاْ فَمَآ أَبۡقَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4835,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wathamūdā famā abqā ","translations":["And Thamud","so not","He spared","(51)"],"transliterationArr":["wathamūdā","famā","abqā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,3500],[3,3500,4855]]}},{"name":"53:52","price":"52. இவர்களுக்கு முன்னர் இருந்த நூஹுடைய மக்களையும் (அழித்தவன் அவன்தான்). நிச்சயமாக இவர்கள் (அனைவரும்) அநியாயக்காரர்களாகவும், வரம்பு மீறியவர்களாகவும் இருந்தனர்.","arabic":"وَقَوۡمَ نُوحٖ مِّن قَبۡلُۖ إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ هُمۡ أَظۡلَمَ وَأَطۡغَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4836,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waqawma nūḥin min qablu innahum kānū hum aẓlama wa-aṭghā ","translations":["And (the) people","(of) Nuh","before","before","Indeed, they","they were","they were","more unjust","and more rebellious","(52)"],"transliterationArr":["waqawma","nūḥin","min","qablu","innahum","kānū","hum","aẓlama","wa-aṭghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1580],[3,1580,3870],[4,3870,4820],[5,4820,6660],[6,6660,7630],[7,7630,7960],[8,7960,9090],[9,9090,10615]]}},{"name":"53:53","price":"53. (லூத்தின் மக்களுடைய) கவிழ்ந்துபோன பட்டிணங்களைப் புரட்டி அடித்தவனும் அவன்தான். ","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُؤۡتَفِكَةَ أَهۡوَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4837,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-mu'tafikata ahwā ","translations":["And the overturned cities","He overthrew","(53)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-mu'tafikata","ahwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1880],[2,1880,2825]]}},{"name":"53:54","price":"54. (அவர்கள் அழிவுற்ற நேரத்தில்) அவர்களைச் சூழ்ந்துகொள்ள வேண்டிய (வேதனையான)து முற்றிலும் அவர்களைச் சூழ்ந்து கொண்டது.","arabic":"فَغَشَّىٰهَا مَا غَشَّىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4838,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faghashāhā mā ghashā ","translations":["So covered them","what","covered","(54)"],"transliterationArr":["faghashāhā","mā","ghashā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1550],[2,1550,2030],[3,2030,3065]]}},{"name":"53:55","price":"55. ஆகவே, (மனிதனே! நீ) உனது இறைவனின் கொடைகளில் எதைத் தான் சந்தேகிக்கிறாய்?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ ءَالَآءِ رَبِّكَ تَتَمَارَىٰ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4839,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fabi-ayyi ālāi rabbika tatamārā ","translations":["Then which (of)","the Favors","(of) your Lord","will you doubt","(55)"],"transliterationArr":["fabi-ayyi","ālāi","rabbika","tatamārā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,3520],[3,3520,4370],[4,4370,6265]]}},{"name":"53:56","price":"56. முன்னர் (மனிதர்களுக்கு) அச்சமூட்டி எச்சரிக்கை செய்த தூதர்களைப் போல் இவரும் ஒரு தூதரே!","arabic":"هَٰذَا نَذِيرٞ مِّنَ ٱلنُّذُرِ ٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4840,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"hādhā nadhīrun mina al-nudhuri al-ūlā ","translations":["This","(is) a warner","from","the warners","the former","(56)"],"transliterationArr":["hādhā","nadhīrun","mina","al-nudhuri","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1790],[3,1790,2960],[4,2960,4720],[5,4720,5935]]}},{"name":"53:57","price":"57. தீவிரமாக வரவேண்டிய (உலக முடிவு) காலம் நெருங்கி விட்டது.","arabic":"أَزِفَتِ ٱلۡأٓزِفَةُ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4841,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"azifati al-āzifatu ","translations":["Has approached","the Approaching Day","(57)"],"transliterationArr":["azifati","al-āzifatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,2585]]}},{"name":"53:58","price":"58. அல்லாஹ்வைத் தவிர வேறு யாரும் அதைத் தடுக்க முடியாது.","arabic":"لَيۡسَ لَهَا مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ كَاشِفَةٌ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4842,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"laysa lahā min dūni al-lahi kāshifatun ","translations":["Not is","for it","besides","besides","Allah","any remover","(58)"],"transliterationArr":["laysa","lahā","min","dūni","al-lahi","kāshifatun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,770],[2,770,1410],[3,1410,2440],[4,2440,3440],[5,3440,4380],[6,4380,5905]]}},{"name":"53:59","price":"59. இதைப் பற்றி நீங்கள் ஆச்சரியப்படுகிறீர்களா?","arabic":"أَفَمِنۡ هَٰذَا ٱلۡحَدِيثِ تَعۡجَبُونَ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4843,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afamin hādhā al-ḥadīthi taʿjabūna ","translations":["Then of","this","statement","you wonder","(59)"],"transliterationArr":["afamin","hādhā","al-ḥadīthi","taʿjabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,1580],[3,1580,2750],[4,2750,5965]]}},{"name":"53:60","price":"60. (இதைப் பற்றி) நீங்கள் சிரிக்கிறீர்களே? அழ வேண்டாமா?","arabic":"وَتَضۡحَكُونَ وَلَا تَبۡكُونَ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4844,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wataḍḥakūna walā tabkūna ","translations":["And you laugh","and (do) not","weep","(60)"],"transliterationArr":["wataḍḥakūna","walā","tabkūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1670],[2,1670,2250],[3,2250,5625]]}},{"name":"53:61","price":"61. (இதைப் பற்றி) நீங்கள் கவலையற்று இருக்கிறீர்களே!","arabic":"وَأَنتُمۡ سَٰمِدُونَ","category":["53 (An-Najm)","An-Najm","Surah An-Najm"],"ayahNumber":4845,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":null,"lan